==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Bordello
<hw>Bor"del*lo</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>a building where
prostitutes are available for hire; a brothel.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> whorehouse, whore house, brothel, bagnio, house of
prostitution, house of ill repute, bawdyhouse, bawdy house, cathouse,
sporting house.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source> + <source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

